{{Disambiguation|link to the alternate page=[[Lighthouse_(Station)|Lighthouse (Station)]]}} {{Place | image1= <gallery> File:Lighthouse Day View.jpg|Day View File:Lighthouse Night.png|Night View File:lighthouse front.png|Front </gallery> | caption-image1=The lighthouse at night. | usage=To guide ships. | closest_station=[[Lighthouse (Station)]] }}
The '''Lighthouse''' is a landmark in game, and allows ships to pass by safely. It is colored in red and white, and has the Union Jack National flag flying above. It is connected to [[Lighthouse (Station)|Lighthouse Station]], though it is not in regular operation. The nearest stations currently in operation include [[Gleethrop End]], [[Dovedale Central]] and [[Pallion Harbour]].
