{{Train|title1=Class 390|image1=[[Class390_1.png]]|top_speed=150 mph|powered_by=Electric|spawn_points=N/A|coaches=6|doors=24|date_added=1st October 2023|status=Admin Only}}
The '''Class 390''' is an admin-only high-speed passenger electric multiple unit (EMU). Reaching a top speed of 150 mph, it is currently the fastest train in the game.
==Gallery== <gallery> File:Class390CabExterior.png|The exterior of one of the cabs of the Class 390. </gallery> [[Category:Trains]] [[Category:Admin Only]]

{{Train | image1= <gallery> File:465 train main.png|Front View File:465 consist.png|Coaches Consist File:465 front.png|Front View 2 </gallery> | caption-image1=A Class 465 in development. | top_speed=75 mph | powered_by= Electric | spawn_points=Unknown | coaches= 4 | doors= 16 per set | date_added=N/A | status=In-development }}
The '''Class 465 ''Networker''''' is an upcoming train that is currently in development. The train is an electric multiple unit (EMU). No release date has been confirmed so far, though it was first leaked on 21 October 2023. It has a top speed of 75 mph, and consists of 4 coaches per train set. It also has an interior with a fitted out cab. [[Category:Trains]]
== Gallery == <gallery> File:456 image sprite 1.png File:456x37.png </gallery>

{{Place | image1= <gallery> File:Dovedale East Bus Terminal.jpg|Day View File:Dovedale East Bus Terminal Night.png|Night View </gallery> | usage=Buses stopping at [[Dovedale East]] | closest_station=[[Dovedale East]] }}
The '''Dovedale East Bus Terminal''' is the bus terminal located at [[Dovedale East]] station.
== Gallery == <gallery> File:Dovedale East Bus Terminal Winter.jpg|The bus terminal during winter. File:Dovedale East Overview Winter.jpg|Overview of [[Dovedale East]] with the bus terminal in the background. </gallery> [[Category:Landmarks]]

[[Category:Level Crossings]] {{Crossing | image1= <gallery> File:Masonfield Crossing.png|Day File:Masonfield Crossing Night.png|Night File:MS Crossing Overview.jpg|Overview </gallery> | singal_box=[[Masonfield Signal Box]] | tracks=4 | road_lanes=2 | gate_operation=Manual | crossing_code=Unknown | nearest_station=[[Masonfield]] | xp_requirment=2500XP }}
'''Masonfield Crossing''' is a ''Manually Controlled Barrier'' level crossing located next to the [[Masonfield Signal Box]]. It was added in Version 1.2, alongside the overhaul of the entire [[Masonfield]] area. It is the signalbox with the most tracks on it, with 4 tracks crossing it.
The crossing is controlled by the adjacent [[Masonfield Signal Box]]. == Gallery ==
